OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FA bomb hoaxer claimed he would target
OL,7,Fa town hall after accusing Andy
OL,8,FBurnham of "protecting paedophiles"
OL,9,Fand threatening MPs, a court has heard.
OL,11,FAnthony McGrath, 57, claimed the bombs
OL,12,Fwould arrive from Russia and added:
OL,13,F"Stop protecting _paedophiles
OL,14,F@AndyBurnhamGM because the town hall
OL,15,Fwill also be removed."
OL,26,@pD@LOUuD@AOUwD@VO]
