CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FPosting on X in November 2025, McGrath
OL,7,Falso threatened Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice headquarters unless they
OL,9,Freturned property belonging to him,
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court heard on Friday
OL,11,F10 July.
OL,13,FIn January and February 2024 he sent a
OL,14,Fseries of threatening emails to
OL,15,Fprofessionals, including Salford MP
OL,16,FRebecca Long-Bailey and Sir Robert
OL,17,FBuckland, who at the time was MP for
OL,18,FSouth Swindon, as well as a judge,
OL,19,Fsolicitor, chartered surveyor and Nat
OL,20,FWest bank strategist.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
