PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FMcGrath, of Sale, Greater Manchester,
OL,7,Fwas given a community order after the
OL,8,Fcourt heard he was suffering with his
OL,9,Fmental health at the time and had been
OL,10,Fsectioned following his arrest.
OL,12,FMartyn Walsh, prosecuting, said in one
OL,13,Femail sent to Ms Long-Bailey, McGrath
OL,14,Fsaid: "You all messed with the wrong
OL,15,Fperson. My army is much bigger
OL,16,Fconsidering I have Russian and Chinese
OL,17,Fsupport. We will be armed and shoot to
OL,18,Fkill."
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@FO]
