OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FIn another message, he told the Labour
OL,7,FMP "you are a target" and gave a time
OL,8,Fwhen her office would explode
OL,10,FMr Walsh told the court: "Ms Long-
OL,11,FBailey said the incident 'made me feel
OL,12,Fworried about the safety of my staff
OL,13,Fand myself'."
OL,15,FMcGrath sent an email with the subject
OL,16,F"car bomb" to Sir Robert, who served
OL,17,Fas a minister in Conservative
OL,18,Fgovernments, and gave a time when he
OL,19,Fsaid the politician's house would
OL,20,F"explode".
