OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FIn an email to district judge
OL,7,FJacqueline White he said: "We have
OL,8,Fevery judge's home address and we also
OL,9,Fhave packs of lions."
OL,11,FThe court heard he also alleged there
OL,12,Fwas a "bomb alert from the IRA" in an
OL,13,Femail to Laurie Burnley-Myers who is
OL,14,Fpart of the Jewish Representative
OL,15,FCouncil for Greater Manchester.
OL,17,FDefending McGrath, Lucy Morgan said:
OL,18,F"It is my submission that there is no
OL,19,Freal risk of this happening again. He
OL,20,Fis now looked after, medicated and in
OL,21,Fremission for his conditions."
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
