OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Gary Woodhall said:
OL,7,F"These offences all occurred, on the
OL,8,Finformation before me, when you were
OL,9,Fsuffering with a mental health
OL,10,Frelapse. If that wasn't the case, the
OL,11,Fsentence in this case would have been
OL,12,Fentirely different."
OL,14,FHe ordered McGrath to carry out a 10-
OL,15,Fday rehabilitation activity
OL,16,Frequirement and complete a 12-month
OL,17,Fmental health treatment requirement as
OL,18,Fpart of his 15-month community order.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TO]
