CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783779570
OL,3,CBomb hoaxer claimed Andy Burnham was
OL,4,C'protecting paedophiles', court told
OL,6,FMcGrath pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,7,Fhearing to one count of sending a
OL,8,Fcommunication threatening death or
OL,9,Fserious harm and 12 counts of sending
OL,10,Fby public communications network an
OL,11,Foffensive/indecent/obscene/menacing
OL,12,Fmessage.
OL,14,FHe was also made subject to
OL,15,Frestraining orders preventing him from
OL,16,Fcommunicating with the people he had
OL,17,Fsent emails to for seven years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
